# Panther
<hr/>

## Requirements
<div class="termy">

```console
Python 3.10+
```
</div>

<hr/>

## Installation

- ### Create Virtual Environment

  * <a href="https://">Linux </a>
  * <a href="https://">Windows </a>
  * <a href="https://">Mac </a>

- ### Install Panther 
    <div class="termy">

    ```console
    $ pip install panter
    ```
    </div>
<hr/>

## Usage
- #### Create Project
    <div class="termy">
    
    ```console
    $ panther create <project_name>
    ```
    </div>
- #### Run Project
    <div class="termy">
    
    ```console
    $ panther run 
    ```
    </div>

